Package MutationTesting

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildConfig  
    Mutation
    Mutation model object This object stores information about one individual possible mutation to a file, including the location (line, character range) of the modification to be made, the old operator and the one it is being replaced with, whether or not the mutation has failed/been killed, and which file the mutation is derived from.
    MutationCompiler  
    MutationReport
    Mutation Report Model Object
    MutationTest
    Mutation Test Model Object
    MutationTestingApp
    The MutationTestingApp class serves as the overall class driving the mutation testing application.
    Mutator
    Abstract class for generating Mutations and creating new files with them
    Program
    Program model object.
    SourceFile
    A subclass of File that knows whether or not it should be mutated
    TestSuite
    Description of TestSuite class Object model of a test suite, which consists of a folder containing any number of test files
    Timing
    provides functionality to measure compile time
